high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sink.
Pick up pepper shaker from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the cabinet to your left.
Place pepper shaker on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Shifting pepper shaker from one place to another.

high_descs: Turn around to reach the sink counter on the left.
Pick up the pepper shaker from the sink counter.
Look down to reach the cabinet under the sink.
Put the pepper shaker in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put the pepper shaker in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn back and walk few steps and turn left to reach the sink
Take a pepper shaker from the top of the sink
Turn back and once again turn back to reach the cabinet which is under the sink
Open the cabinet and put the pepper shaker in it and close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the pepper shaker in the cabinet
